The 'Qatar national football team' is the national team of Qatar and is
controlled by the Qatar Football Association. They have never qualified for a
FIFA World Cup but are hosting the 2022 FIFA World Cup. The team has also
appeared in seven AFC Asian Cup tournaments and hosted the 2011 AFC Asian Cup.
